description:
Today Adam and Sophie sit down to paint Sophie's first ever Warhammer miniature! Sophie has decided to dive straight into Warhammer 40,000 Kill Team and Adam has a few tips and tricks to help her with her painting journey.

So sit back, relax and enjoy the shared experience of painting for the first time!
